            "name": "Fumadocs Export the search index for static/client-side search",
            "description": {
              "content": "Exports the full search index database so that client-side search implementations can download and query it locally without making per-query requests. The response format depends on the underlying search engine (Orama, Flexsearch, etc.) configured by the site. This endpoint path is a convention; actual path may vary per documentation site.",
